            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001382_0001" n="0001"/>

<opener>  
<lb/><salute>Dear <persName>Thornton</persName>,</salute>
</opener>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">A <term type="animal">hippo</term> - has been
<lb/>shot <measure>7 miles</measure> above
<lb/>you - We go on
<lb/>to the high hill
<lb/>today (<date when="1858-11-29">Monday 29</date>)
<lb/>and return to
<lb/>some men left
<lb/>here to cut up
<lb/>the meat either
<lb/>this evening or
<lb/>tomorrow <w>morn<supplied>-</supplied>
<lb break="no"/>-ing</w>. I send
<lb/>a piece of meat.
<lb/>Either come
<lb/>or remain

	<pb facs="liv_001382_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>where you are
<lb/>as you think
<lb/>best - I hope
<lb/>you are now
<lb/>recovered -</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><persName><choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>David</expan></choice> Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><postscript><p rend="no-indent">Supposing you
<lb/>remain send
<lb/>some to cut
<lb/>up &amp; dry &amp;
<lb/>carry down
<lb/>meat</p></postscript>



            </div>
        </body>
